    "for fil in files:\n",
    "    mask = xr.open_dataset(fil)\n",
    "    print(mask)\n",
    "    bs_name = os.path.basename(fil)\n",
    "    var = bs_name.split('.')\n",
    "    print(var)\n",
    "    _vars = mask.variables\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if 'source_code' in _vars:\n",
    "        mask = mask.drop('source_code')\n",
    "        \n",
    "    if 'receptor_code' in _vars:\n",
    "        print(mask.variables)\n",
    "        mask = mask.drop('receptor_code')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    mask = mask.where(mask==1, int(0))\n",
    "    #print(binary)\n",
    "    enc_dict = {str(var[0]):{'zlib': 'True', 'compression_opts': 9}}\n",
    "    #print(enc_dict)\n",
    "    mask.to_netcdf(save_dir + bs_name, engine = 'h5netcdf', encoding = enc_dict)"
   ]

    "writen_files = glob.glob(save_dir + '*.nc')\n",
    "for fil in writen_files:\n",
    "    mask = xr.open_dataset(fil)\n",
    "    bs_name = os.path.basename(fil)\n",
    "    var = bs_name.split('.')[0]\n",
    "    mask[var].plot()\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]

    "def plot_region(lat, lon, region):\n",
    "    desired_projections = [ccrs.PlateCarree()]\n",
    "\n",
    "    fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows=1, ncols=1,\n",
    "                             figsize=(12,15), \n",
    "                             sharex=True, sharey=True, \n",
    "                             subplot_kw = dict(projection=ccrs.PlateCarree()))\n",
    "\n",
    "    # ccrs.RotatedPole(pole_latitude=45, pole_longitude=180)]\n",
    "\n",
    "    # xy is The bottom and left rectangle coordinates\n",
    "\n",
    "    for plot_num, desired_proj in enumerate(desired_projections):\n",
    "\n",
    "        ax = plt.subplot(2, 1, plot_num + 1, projection=desired_proj)\n",
    "\n",
    "        ax.set_global()\n",
    "\n",
    "        ax.add_patch(mpatches.Rectangle(xy=[lon[0], lat[0]], width=np.subtract(lon[1], lon[0]), \n",
    "                                        height=np.subtract(lat[1], lat[0]),\n",
    "                                        facecolor='blue',\n",
    "                                        alpha=0.2,\n",
    "                                        transform=ccrs.PlateCarree())\n",
    "                     )\n",
    "        import cartopy.feature as cfeature\n",
    "        states_provinces = cfeature.NaturalEarthFeature(category='cultural',\n",
    "                                                name='admin_0_boundary_lines_land',\n",
    "                                                scale='50m',\n",
    "                                                facecolor='none')\n",
    "        ax.add_feature(states_provinces, edgecolor='gray')\n",
    "        \n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        ax.add_patch(mpatches.Rectangle(xy=[lon[0], lat[0]], width=np.subtract(lon[1], lon[0]), \n",
    "                                        height=np.subtract(lat[1], lat[0]),\n",
    "                                        facecolor='red',\n",
    "                                        alpha=0.2,\n",
    "                                        transform=ccrs.Geodetic())\n",
    "                     )\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        ax.set_title(\" {}, lon_range {}, lat_range{}\".format(region, lon, lat))\n",
    "        ax.gridlines()\n",
    "        ax.coastlines()\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    return "
   ]
  },
